modName: Tales of Lycanthropy - Werewolf Overhaul - Russian

descriptionHtml:
[color=orange]Attention![/color]

This is just russian translation of the original mod. All credit goes to it\'s creator Brevi.
You can find the original mod at [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12687]this page[/url].

If you like this translation or this mod and want to endorse me, go to [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12687]original mod\'s page[/url] and ENDORSE IT\'S AUTHOR, he did much harder and greater work than this translation.

Detailed russian description & instructions [url=https://docs.google.com/document/pub?id=1UcIsrr1RzRr82pSuqXkIyjAuzks8jWKC8i3ngBznkcM]HERE[/url].
